  <li><strong>Payment Confirmation</strong>: Subject to the  modes of payment chosen by the Seller, in case of payment by Payment on  Billing, upon successful receipt of the Transaction Price by the Company from  the Buyer within [3] days of booking the Transaction and completion of  verification of payment, the Company shall notify the buyer and the seller that  the Transaction Price has been received. In case of payment by Payment on  Delivery, the Company shall notify the buyer and seller that the buyer has  committed to pay the Transaction Price by Payment on Delivery.</li>
